STATE EX REL. LEMASTERS
v.
TWELFTH DIST. COURT OF APPEALS 2019-0480 Supreme Court of Ohio. June 26, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, Donnelly, and Stewart, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Prohibition. On respondent Twelfth District Court of Appeals' motion to dismiss and amended motion to dismiss of respondent Madison County Prosecutor's Office and respondent Judge James A. Brogan. Motions granted. Cause dismissed.
